      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Norbert Raimund Leisner</b>\n</p><p><b>Norbert Raimund Leisner</b>,<br />\na German computer chess aficionado, collector of own compiled chess engines and tester. \nHe serves as editor in <a href=\"/Ron_Murawski\" title=\"Ron Murawski\">Ron Murawski's</a> <i>Computer-Chess Wiki</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, \nand is frequent poster in <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Computer Chess Forums</a>, mostly providing informations on chess engines and engine updates.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2008_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2008 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Norbert_Raimund_Leisner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2008_...\">2008 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Norbert_Raimund_Leisner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2008 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=21887\">Echelon chess engine by Scott Gasch</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 21, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=23477\">Computer Chess Wiki</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 03, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=26548\">Computer-Chess Wikipedia: Native/Linux/Macintosh List</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 13, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=28635\">WBEC-Ridderkerk \"Engine, details\" - Updates</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 25, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/WBEC\" title=\"WBEC\">WBEC</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Norbert_Raimund_Leisner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=37126\">UCI-compatible interface for 10x8 chess?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 17, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=40949\">ComputerChess-Wikipedia</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 31, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=47084\">Mac OS X chess engines - digital signature for Apple?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 02, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Mac_OS\" title=\"Mac OS\">Mac OS</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=48624\">Chess under Linux</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 12, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Linux\" title=\"Linux\">Linux</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50291\">ChessBase / Fritz interface running on Ubuntu?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 17, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Fritz\" title=\"Fritz\">Fritz</a>, <a href=\"/Linux\" title=\"Linux\">Linux</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50523\">Syzygybases suitable for win32-systems?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 17, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50916\">C# compiler for Windows XP SP3</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 15, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/C_sharp\" title=\"C sharp\">C#</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Norbert_Raimund_Leisner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58105\">Halloween-Gambit (Four Knights Game)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Halloween\">October 31</a>, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Brause\" title=\"Brause\">Brause</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=60961\">CCRL - CEGT matches</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 28, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/CCRL\" title=\"CCRL\">CCRL</a>, <a href=\"/CEGT\" title=\"CEGT\">CEGT</a>, <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Opening Book</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=65218\">Stockfish Chess 8 - en passant rule</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 19, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/En_passant\" title=\"En passant\">En passant</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=66023\">75 moves FIDE-rule in section 9.6b</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 16, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Fifty-move_Rule\" title=\"Fifty-move Rule\">Fifty-move Rule</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=66647\">a question to performance test - perft</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 20, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Perft\" title=\"Perft\">Perft</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67007\">Etherbench and Fishtest</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 03, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67697\">CCWiki Engine List - broken and obsolete links</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 11, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=68073\">CCWiki Lists</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 25, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69500\">New Releases for 2019 - CCWiki</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 05, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=71339\">MacOS for RuyDOS, Sapeli, Scorpio, Topple Chess</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 22, 2019</li></ul>\n<h1>